text: Kathleen Wilhoite (born June 29, 1964) is an American movie and television actress. She has been in lots of movies and television programs. She played Liz Danes in the TV drama Gilmore Girls. She also played Chloe in the medical drama ER. Wilhoite was born in California. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from California
